<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>tiripuvanac cakkarattikaḷ kulōttuṅka cōḻa tēvaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="27">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num>
<lb n="2"/>vatu ceyaciṅka kulakāla vaḷaṉāṭṭuk kuḷamaṅkala nāṭṭuc cempāṭāṉa cempiya
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṉ puttāmpūr Uṭaiyār tiruvaiyāṟuṭaiya nāyaṉār kōyil muppatu vaṭṭa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ttu civappirāmaṇarōm Uṭaiyār tiruvaiyāruṭaiya nāyaṉāṟku Oru ca
<lb n="5" break="no"/>nti Amutupaṭikku Upaiyamākak kaikkoṇṭa nilam periyā vayakka
<lb n="6" break="no"/>lum kaṟṟaiyum muṟikamumaṟañciyaṉ vayakkaluṅ kaikkoṇṭu cantirāti
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ttavarai Oru canti nāṉāḻi Arici celuttakkaṭavōmāka kaikkoṇṭōm § 
</p>

